{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they took us over the Elba and that-- and then somehow in a circle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We went round and around in a circle for 10 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I don't know how many bridges we crossed or the same bridges.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't remember anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I only know that on the tenth day we were camped on the other side of the Elba, because by that time it was already clear.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "On this side were the Americans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And, by the way, during the death march the German guards put on striped prison clothing so that they shouldn't be seen as separate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And the Americans were low flying, so low flying that we waved to them constantly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And they were accompanying us the whole way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And when we went over the Elba, then there were Russians on the other side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And they were low flying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we were in a forest next to the Elba.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And that night we camped in a clearing in the forest and they slaughtered a horse and gave us pieces of raw meat, raw horse meat, and also and a handful of raw rice.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we ate it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Again we had dysentery.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We were ill.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We were weak.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And during this death march, anybody who collapsed, anybody-- and there were very many-- they were shot on the spot and left there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we were always less and less who walked on, who carried on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "But we carried on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And after that night the Russians circulated with low flying airplanes, circulated us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And then in the morning, early in the morning, the guards woke us up and they said we are going back on the same bridge on which we came.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And it was dark when we started, and as we walked there was a sunrise.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
